        <mxCell id="metrics-content" value="• Face Embedding: 2622-D vector (VGG-Face)&#xa;• Vector Search: IVFFlat index, cosine similarity&#xa;• Liveness Score: 0.0 - 1.0 (threshold: 0.5)&#xa;• Match Score: 0.0 - 1.0 (threshold: 0.6)&#xa;• EAR Threshold: 0.2 (blink detection)&#xa;• MAR Threshold: 0.6 (smile detection)&#xa;• Video Stream: 30 FPS via WebSocket&#xa;• NFC: ISO 7816-4 APDU commands" style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=10;fontColor=#4a5568;spacingLeft=5;" parent="1" vertex="1">
